		"product_comparison": "Product Comparison: Allows customers to compare features, prices, and specifications of products before making a purchase decision.",
		"one-click_purchase": "One-Click Purchase: Simplifies the checkout process by allowing customers to complete purchases with a single click.",
		"order_tracking": "Order Tracking: Enables customers to track the status of their orders in real-time.",
		"abandoned_cart_recovery": "Abandoned Cart Recovery: Sends reminders to customers who have added items to their cart but not completed the purchase.",
